dct_title_s: A township map of the State of Iowa
dct_description_sm: Showing the streams, roads, towns, post offices, county seats, works of internal improvements, &c., &c., &c.   Shows township and range, as well as railroads, common roads, dams, ferries and land offices.   "Henn, Williams & Co.'s land, exchange & banking houses in Fairfield and Chariton, Iowa; Henn, Williams Hooton & Co. in Council Bluffs Iowa."
